    NOTE: You may also read Rainboot 2.30`s @{"news" LINK Firs}!


    Hi!
    
    After a long time of hard work, I am finally proud to present you
    the new generation of Rainboot - Rainboot3. It's more than just
    a major update; so much things have been reworked and there are
    many new features including cool Multimedia ones, so that the
    new Rainboot3 slogan is "Multimedia Has Got A Name". Just have a
    look at the demos to see what you can do now with Rainboot. Multiple
    anims, cycles, modules, user controls, screen wipes etc. is no
    more a problem for your favourite multimedia viewer!

    Due to this really major update, I've also to ask the registered
    users for a small upgrade fee, which actually is 10 DM/8$ US-Dollars. 
    If you pay this fee, you'll get your personal Rainboot3 full version.
    All other users have to register for the regular fee. The upgrade
    is a special price for all Rainboot 2.x registered users.
     
    Now have much fun with Rainboot3 and please register your copy!
    Your support means a lot to me! Really.
    
    Thank you,
    
    yours kindly,
    
    Andreas Falkenhahn

    --    
    Andreas Falkenhahn (aka Software Failure of Airsoft Softwair)
    Coder, Powered up with Amiga 1200T, Blizzard T-ERC 68040,
    http://www.airsoftsoftwair.de/  · ICQ: 42908277 ·  IRC: SFA

