    · complete the WINDOW emulation mode (add support for anim brush remapping)
    · add support for normal ANIM(5,6,7,8) animations
    · more commands & effects

    Please drop me a @{"mail" LINK Credits} if you have some nice ideas
    what shall be implemented/changed in Rainboot 3.
    
